programme.title: The Morgenland Festival
programme.sub-title: The Morgenland Festival: The Art of Duo
programme.desc: Since 2005, the Morgenland Festival of Osnabrueck has dedicated itself to the fascinating music culture of the Near and Middle East. From traditional and classical music to avant-garde, jazz, and rock, the festival program also features art, such as visual arts, dance, and theatre of interdisciplinary projects. "The Art of Duo" presents an unprecedented duo featuring pianist Salman Gambarov and sheng player, a Chinese mouth-organ, Wu Wei.

programme.title: Aki Rissanen Trio at Jazzclub Unterfahrt, Munich
programme.desc: Aki Rissanens interest in jazz came after he started taking classical piano lessons. His deep interest in improvised music placed him among top jazz pianist in his home country - Finland. While composing and performing his own music, Rissanen has also collaborated with Verneri Pohjola and Dave Liebman, and today his name appears among the top European jazz musicians. Live from "Jazzclub Unterfahrt" in Munich, Germany, together with Antti Lotjonen on bass and Teppo Makynen on drums, Rissanen showcases the best of Scandinavian jazz and its DNA - the Nordic Tone.

programme.title: Ella Fitzgerald in Brussels
programme.sub-title: Ella Fitzgerald in Brussels: The American Songbook
programme.desc: Ella Fitzgerald: Live in "57" features "The First Lady Of Song" in a distinct performance. Its the earliest known complete concert of Ella to be captured on film. Shot in Belgium, this 1957 concert sees her performing with jazz greats Ray Brown, Herb Ellis, Jo Jones and the legendary Oscar Peterson on classics such as "Lullaby Of Birdland" and It Dont Mean A Thing (If It Aint Got That Swing). Although she wanted to be a dancer at first, Ella Fitzgerald already listened to recordings of Louis Armstrong, Bing Crosby and The Boswell Sisters at an early age. After her debut at an amateur talent show in 1934, Ella joined Chick Webbs Orchestra with which she recorded several hits; after Webb died, she became the leader of the orchestra. In the late 1940s, Ella Fitzgerald became known as the First Lady of Song, with her wide vocal range of three octaves. The American jazz singer was particularly appreciated for her pure tone, intonation and phrasing, and unparalleled improvisational abilities. In a career that spanned close to 60 years, Fitzgerald sold 40 million albums and won 13 Grammy Awards, mainly for her definitive interpretations of the Great American Songbook.

programme.title: Live at the Metro Theatre
programme.desc: Angus and Julia Stone are an Australian brother-sister folk-blues group which formed in 2006. Their parents played as a folk duo before Julia and Angus were born. Angus and Julia Stone have released two studio albums, A Book Like This (8 September 2007), which peaked at No. 6 on the ARIA Albums Chart; and Down. Here they perform at The Metro Theatre, in Sydney, Australia, on October 10, 2007.

programme.title: DJAZZ Portrait
programme.desc: These portraits of artists, concerts and festivals give a good impression of the jazz world. Both famous and less famous jazz artists will give a new insight in their life. DJAZZ asked them why they wrote that special song, what was the first record they bought and what is his or her most precious musical memory. The festival portraits are beautiful reports filmed at the most special jazz festivals and concerts. They revive the memory of the festival, the music and the experience.

programme.title: Dionne Warwick live at the 27 Club
programme.desc: Dionne Warwicks vocal artistry ranges from voluminous deep register to soft, fragile high notes. She masters the entire range with almost unnerving ease. But more than her strong, warm voice, Dionnes magic is in the silky elegance and the secure delivery with which she tells a story. Thats how her, along with composer Burt Bacharach and lyricist Hal David become pioneers of the brand of pop music called "Middle of the Road", meaning pop that is grippingly simple, but never trite. Sixty of her hits made it into the American charts and sold over 100 million albums worldwide. This amazing 1964 recording from the 27 Club in Knokke, Belgium showcases the 23-year-old star vocalist at the start of her career.

programme.title: Terrasson and Belmondo
programme.sub-title: Terrasson and Belmondo: À Nous Garo
programme.desc: Every year, the Jazz en Baie festival takes place in the beautiful bay of Mont Saint-Michel Todays broadcast shows a special gathering between two grandmasters of French jazz: pianist Jacky Terrasson and trumpeter Stephane Belmondo. The two team up for an amazing concert in which jazz is combined with soul and a touch of chanson française. The Franco-American pianist Terrasson delights in travelling the world, collaboration with others and leading his own trio, quartet, or quintet. With his long-time friend, Stephane Belmondo, Terrasson has produced wonderful CDs and beautiful concerts. One then finds the trumpeter on the pianists album Gouache; on another, the pianist guests on Belmondos Ever After. At the Jazz en Baie festival, the duo plays its amazing piano and trumpet music. Highly recommended!

programme.title: BIRD - The Nest
programme.desc: Five promising musicians get together in Rotterdam jazz club BIRDs artists-in-residence project "The Nest". Over the course of seven sessions, these talents exchange ideas, work on their projects, and play music together. Following this period, during which record producer Jameszoo and music manager Jochem Tromp offer their coaching experience, BIRD and North Sea Jazz Festivals fringe festival DownTown organize a tryout performance. In this short documentary, the artists share their impressions from the project. They introduce themselves, reveal why they joined The Nest and formulate what they hope to learn from the experience. Naturally, we get a glimpse of the songs they wrote during the sessions, as performed during the tryout show. Featuring Lisette Ma Neza (slam poet), Peter Somuah (trumpet), Michelle Samba (drums), Huy Le (bass), and Brenn Luiten (piano).

programme.title: Jazzwoche Burghausen
programme.desc: Every year since 1970, the German city of Burghausen has been hosting one of the largest jazz festivals in the world. During Burghausen International Jazz Week, Burghausen becomes a Bavarian jazz mecca: guests from all over the world join the Burghausers to enjoy the most wonderful jazz performances as the colorful hustle and bustle of spectators and musicians shake up the city. One of the bands performing here in 2019 is the Walter Trout Band. Trout, who was born in New Jersey and is based in Los Angeles, is a world-famous contemporary blues rock guitarist and vocalist.

programme.title: Jungle By Night - Jazz in Duketown
programme.desc: Jazz in Duketown is the largest free outdoor jazz festival in the Netherlands. Its a real gathering for jazz addicts, inviting internationally renowned bands. In 2019, one of them is the Amsterdam-based Dutch instrumental collective Jungle by Night. The band plays a mix of various styles, inspired by funk, jazz, dub, rock and others. The ensemble made its debut in 2010 and has played at numerous festivals. Their December 2010 performance with former backing musicians of Afrobeat founder Fela Kuti in Paris saw them hailed as "the future of Afrobeat".

programme.title: Arsenik - Olympia, Paris
programme.desc: The mythical duo Arsenik is a rap group from France, made up of two brothers, Lino and Calbo. The team performs at Olympia Paris to celebrate their 20 years since their first album, Quelques gouttes suffisent… Its a unique concert: Arsenik plays the entire album with numerous special guests for the first time. The album has sold over 300,000 copies in France. Today its being considered a classic, and it continues to be cited in the top five of the best French rap albums of all generations. Enjoy Arseniks live show in Olympia Paris!

programme.title: Woody Hermans Swinging Herd live in England 1964
programme.desc: Woody Herman: Live in 64 features a blistering one-hour concert from 1964 showcasing one of the very hottest line-ups of the "Swinging Herd," including trumpeter Bill Chase, trombonist Phil Wilson, and the amazing saxophonist Sal Nistico on the front line, as well as drummer Jake Hanna, bassist Chuck Andrus, and pianist-arranger Nat Pierce in the rhythm section. The band roars throughout the entire show which includes standards such as "Lonesome Old Town", "After Youve Gone", and new originals including Charles Minguss "Better Git It In Your Soul."

programme.title: NSJ Big Band Show
programme.sub-title: NSJ Big Band Show: Skymasters and Dizzy Gillespie
programme.desc: The world-renowned North Sea Jazz Festival features a wide variety of genres, including traditional New Orleans jazz, swing, bop, free jazz, fusion, avant-garde and electronic jazz, blues, gospel, funk, soul, RandB, hip hop, world beat and Latin. The festival was founded by entrepreneur and jazz fan Paul Acket, who sold his highly successful pop magazine publishing house to organize and fund the first edition of the festival in 1976. This broadcast from the North Sea Jazz Archives presents the amazing Dizzy Gillespie, accompanied by The Skymasters.

programme.title: Tribute to Django Reinhardt
programme.sub-title: Tribute to Django Reinhardt: Bireli Lagrene
programme.desc: Bireli Lagrène is a French jazz guitarist born on September 4, 1966 in a family of gypsy tradition. His brother and his father introduced him from an early age to the repertoire of Django Reinhardt, whose influence is still felt in the style of Lagrène. In this performance, Lagrène pays homage to Django Reinhardt with his son, Babik Reinhardt.

programme.title: Dave Brubeck and Paul Desmond live in Belgium
programme.desc: Dave Brubeck: Live in 64 boasts a beautifully filmed concert from one of the most beloved quartets in jazz history. Captured at the pinnacle of their power and popularity, Paul Desmond (alto sax), Joe Morello (drums), Eugene Wright (bass) and Dave Brubeck (piano) explore the trails they blazed into the realm of odd time signatures with "Forty Days" and two versions of their groundbreaking hit Take Five, as well as forays into world music with a unique interpretation of Koto Song. Their intimate onstage chemistry and impeccable musicianship made the DBQ an award-winning jazz supergroup.

programme.title: WOMEX 2018
programme.desc: Since 1994, World Music Expo (WOMEX) has been attracting musicians, agents, a great number of press agencies, as well as media companies from all over the world. Its main exposition event has been held in various locations throughout Europe, including Berlin, Brussels, Marseille, Stockholm, Seville, Cardiff, and Budapest. In 2018, WOMEX was held in Las Palmas, Gran Canaria.

programme.title: La nuit des gitans
programme.desc: The Royal Conservatoire of Liège hosted a "Night of the Gypsies" at the International Guitar Festival of Liège in 1995. At this occasion, the Raphaël Faÿs Trio and Quintet paid tribute to Romani-Belgian jazz guitarist Django Reinhardt. Raphaël Faÿs (solo guitar), Pierre Blanchard (violin), Daniel Manzanas (guitar), Pablo Gilabert (bass) and Miguel Sanchez (percussion) play Reinhardts greatest gypsy jazz hits, including It Had To Be You, How High The Moon, Sweet Georgia Brown, and Minor Swing. Enjoy Raphaël Faÿss fresh take on the light-fingered string sound and swinging rhythms of Django Reinhardts gypsy jazz!

programme.title: Louis "Satchmo" Armstrong and His All Stars
programme.desc: Louis Armstrong: Live in 59 is one of the only known complete Armstrong concerts from the 1950s to be captured on film. This 55-minute set, filmed in Belgium in 1959, features many of Satchmos greatest songs including Mack The Knife, When Its Sleepy Time Down South and "Stompin" At The Savoy, backed by his stellar band the All-Stars, featuring Trummy Young, Peanuts Hucko, Billy Kyle, Danny Barcelona and Mort Herbert.

programme.title: Piano and Sax
programme.sub-title: Piano and Sax: Charlie Mariano and Wolfgang Dauner
programme.desc: Piano and saxophone - this is an individualistic jazz duo combination. But the melodiousness and maturity of Charlie Marianos saxophone and the freshness and feistiness of Wolfgang Dauners piano turn the meeting of these two jazz greats into a thrilling interplay.

programme.title: Seine Sessions
programme.desc: Jam session dates brought back to the 1920s, when white and black musicians sought out a smoky bar after their paid performances to play the jazz they didnt get the chance to do in their Paul Whiteman style bands.

programme.title: The Morgenland Festival
programme.desc: Since 2005, the Morgenland Festival of Osnabrueck has dedicated itself to the fascinating music culture of the Near and Middle East. From traditional and classical music to avant-garde, jazz, and rock, the festival program also features art, such as visual arts, dance, and theatre of interdisciplinary projects. "Viva" is a perfect mixture of various instruments and musicians from all over the world. Vocalists Aynur and Dima Oshno perform with the All Star Band. Aynur sings about the life and sufferings of Kurdish people, in particular Kurdish women. Musically, she tries to blend Kurdish and Western music, creating her own style and interpreting the traditional repertoire in a modern and fresh way.

programme.title: Sarah Vaughan Live in 58 and 64
programme.sub-title: Sarah Vaughan Live in 58 and 64: The Divine One
programme.desc: Sarah Vaughan: Live in 58 and 64 features the "Divine One" in her prime, wrapping her sultry voice around jazz standards such as Lover Man, "Misty" and "I Got Rhythm" and soaring on popular showtunes such as "Over The Rainbow" and Maria. One of the greatest voices of the 20th Century, her renditions of songs by Harold Arlen, Leonard Bernstein, Johnny Burke, the Gershwins and Stephen Sondheim are pure diva magic. These three performances demonstrate why Sarah Vaughan is invariably mentioned in the same breath as Ella Fitzgerald and Billie Holiday.

programme.title: Georgie Fame and the Blue Flames
Milt Jacksons Modern Jazz Quartet at the Bozar
programme.desc: The Modern Jazz Quartet (MJQ) was composed of Milt "Bags" Jackson on vibraphone, John Lewis on piano, Percy Heath on bass, and Connie Kay on drums. Milt Jackson and John Lewis were pioneer bebop musicians who had played together in Dizzy Gillespies 1948 big band. They pursued separate careers before adding Heath and Lewis to form the Modern Jazz Quartet in the 1950s. Noted for its delicate percussion sonorities, innovative jazz forms, and high performance standards, the MJQ was an immensely popular jazz and "third stream" ensemble until its final concerts in the early 1990s.

programme.title: La Mambanegra - Music Meeting Festival 2018
programme.desc: The latin music orchestra, La Mambanegra, combines many musical elements, such as Jamaican or Colombian music, as well as Funk and Hip Hop. Yet, their main musical influence comes from 1970s New York, where during the time Salsa was born. The magic of the genre, however, is given new colours by La Mambanegra: with a series of fantastic adventures in Cali, La Habana and New York, the bands music is inspired by an anonymous and even mythical hero of the Calis popular neighborhood Barrio Obrero. Consisting of 8 talented musicians, La Mambanegra presents their charming showcase at the Music Meeting Festival in Nijmegen, The Netherlands.

programme.title: Michelle David - Jazz in Duketown
programme.desc: Jazz in Duketown is the largest free outdoor jazz festival in the Netherlands. Its a real gathering for jazz addicts, inviting internationall renowned artists. The talented American singer Michelle David performs pop and gospel music that feeds the heart and soothes the soul. Having grown up with the church, she started singing at the age of four. A year later she joined her first band, The Mission of Love. In 1980 she enrolled at Fiorello H. LaGuardia High School of Music and Art and Performing Arts in New York City, known from the film Fame. During this time, she appeared as an extra in the legendary comedy film Ghostbusters. Musicals and tours with the bands of Diana Ross and Michael Bolton followed.

programme.title: Duets
programme.sub-title: Duets: Carla Bley and Steve Swallow in 1988
programme.desc: If any two musicians share a special bond when they perform, its pianist Carla Bley and bassist Steve Swallow. The two have performed in the same bands since the 1960s and have been romantic partners for more than two decades. Watching them perform is the definition of musical telepathy. A glance or a smile seems to change the feel of the music. In 1988, Swallow and Bley began performing duet concerts in Europe, United States, South America and Japan. This performance of Duets, their album of songs arranged for piano and bass, was released that same year. The performance showcases their approach to traditional jazz, folk and classical music, as well as their poignant musical story.

programme.title: Rebirth
programme.desc: Amsterdam, February 6th, 2018 - The short documentary Rebirth in The Amsterdam Red Light District illustrates how brutal Richard Lems life as an addict was and his struggle to unshackle himself from the shame. Filled with fierce, freighting, and sad moments, Richard relives his stabbing, stay in jail, drug test, and drug use. Richard expresses himself verbally but mainly relives the moments through drumming, which renders the documentary an intense and unique experience. Addiction doctor and musician Gerard Alderliefste: "If he dares to bottom out, he will see it was the drugs and not himself. Music can bring those emotions to the surface".

programme.title: Jim Hall and Atilla Zoller - Extensions
programme.desc: This selection of unforgettable performances by some of the most iconic and influential jazz guitarists in history showcases these legends unique essence. Revel in Wes Montgomerys virtuosity as he performs the captivating "Nicas Dream" in Holland in 1965, and delight in the expressive beauty of his rendition of "Heres That Rainy Day", recorded in London in that same year. Experience the timeless appeal of Joe Passs "You Stepped Out of a Dream" and "You Turned The Tables on Me", recorded live in Hanover in 1975. The interplay between Jim Hall and Atilla Zoller borders on the impossible as they perform "Extensions" in Hanover in 1973. Enjoy Jim Halls lyrical solo performance of "Im Getting Sentimental Over You" from 1964. Witness Sonny Sharrocks avant-garde fusion of jazz and rock in an exhilarating performance of "Peanut", recorded live in France in 1970. Sharrock is joined by flutist Herbie Mann in a soulful performance of "Memphis Underground" from 1969. Immerse yourself in the magic of jazz guitar!

programme.title: Paradox Live
programme.sub-title: Paradox Live: Bertus Borgers and The Young Retros
programme.desc: Innovative contemporary jazz and improvised music, the search for modernity, mind blowing sounds, rock and pop… Indeed PARADOX Tilburg goes beyond jazz, crossing musical boundaries into the unknown soundscapes of electronic music. Indie artists, blues veterans and jazz superstars all pour their hearts and souls at the Paradox. From young, local talents to top national and international artists, PARADOX Tilburg is the most intimate jazz club in the Netherlands, with a devoted audience from all across Europe. In their TV show PARADOX LIVE you get a taste of the greatest concerts and interviews with artists from all around the world. This episode of PARADOX LIVE presents the Tilburg based Bertus Borgers and his Young Retros!

programme.title: Wynton in the South Bank Show
programme.desc: Considered one of the most technically brilliant players in the history of the trumpet, jazz musician Wynton Marsalis is also a master of classical music and a fine composer. Marsalis takes the cameras with him around New York, to his home town of New Orleans, and to his rehearsal studios where he and his assembled band of musicians are seen putting together the album Blood on the Fields. He also talks about his music and his way of working.

programme.title: PC Qwintett
programme.desc: Pierre Courbois has been one of Europes leading jazz musicians since the mid-sixties. This concert, recorded at the renowned Amsterdam jazz club Bimhuis, sees the drummer playing with his QWINTETT. On the occasion of his 75th birthday in 2015, Courbois hit the road for the Pierre Courbois 75 Years Anniversary Tour. The PC QWINTETT consists of several highly acclaimed Dutch jazz musicians with whom Courbois has worked before in his long and versatile career. Among them are pianist Nike Langenhuijsen, double bassist Egon Kracht, trumpeter Toon de Gouw, and trombonist Ilja Reijngoud. QWINTETT honours the Charles Mingus tradition of thematic and melodic ensemble jazz - but also with an unmistakable Courbois groove! Courbois, known for his own way of combining compositions with improvisations, melodically melts constructions with uneven breaks.

programme.title: B.B. King
programme.sub-title: B.B. King: The King of the Blues in Stuttgart
programme.desc: This uptempo, funky performance proves that B.B. King, one of the Masters of the Blues Guitar has still got it. The band features some of todays best blues musicians playing all of B.B. Kings classic songs.

programme.title: WOMEX 2018
programme.desc: Since 1994, World Music Expo (WOMEX) has been attracting musicians, agents, a great number of press agencies, as well as media companies from all over the world. Its main exposition event has been held in various locations throughout Europe, including Berlin, Brussels, Marseille, Stockholm, Seville, Cardiff, and Budapest. In 2018, WOMEX was held in Las Palmas, Gran Canaria.

programme.title: Sammy Price and the Harlem Beggars
programme.desc: Pianist, singer and civil rights activist Sammy Price is joined by the gospel singers known as the Harlem Beggars for spirited renditions of "Go Tell It on the Mountain," "Im a Soldier," and "When the Saints Go Marching In," among several others. The group is joined by Wilbert Harrison, who provides accompaniment on organ.

programme.title: The MotorMusic Jazz Sessions
programme.desc: In this unique series,The MotorMusic Studios in Mechelen, Belgium, exert a magnetic attraction on countless first class jazz musicians. Where many of them visit international jazz musicians who share their views of their music with us.

programme.title: DJAZZ Clips
programme.desc: An extraordinary collection of clips in all jazz genres from the most beautiful concerts and the most special festivals, performed by the finest jazz musicians.

programme.title: Marion Williams Sings Spirituals
programme.desc: You cant help but be carried away by the powerful voice Marion Williams, who, with backing from Tommy Brown (piano), Joe Washington (organ), Billy Tuliver (drums), and singers Barbara White and Ann Bolden, sings gospel songs and spirituals as if she has lived them a thousand times over. The repertoire includes such familiar tunes as "Peace in the Valley," "We Shall Overcome," and "Michael, Row the Boat Ashore."

programme.title: Aki Rissanen Trio at Jazzclub Unterfahrt, Munich
programme.desc: Aki Rissanens interest in jazz came after he started taking classical piano lessons. His deep interest in improvised music placed him among top jazz pianist in his home country - Finland. While composing and performing his own music, Rissanen has also collaborated with Verneri Pohjola and Dave Liebman, and today his name appears among the top European jazz musicians. Live from "Jazzclub Unterfahrt" in Munich, Germany, together with Antti Lotjonen on bass and Teppo Makynen on drums, Rissanen showcases the best of Scandinavian jazz and its DNA - the Nordic Tone.

programme.title: DJAZZ Clips
programme.desc: An extraordinary collection of clips in all jazz genres from the most beautiful concerts and the most special festivals, performed by the finest jazz musicians.

programme.title: Jazzwoche Burghausen
programme.desc: Every year since 1970, the German city of Burghausen has been hosting one of the largest jazz festivals in the world. During Burghausen International Jazz Week, Burghausen becomes a Bavarian jazz mecca: guests from all over the world join the Burghausers to enjoy the most wonderful jazz performances as the colorful hustle and bustle of spectators and musicians shake up the city. One of the bands performing here in 2019 is the Hypnotic Brass Ensemble, which consists of eight sons of jazz trumpeter and one-time Sun Ra Arkestra member Phil Cohran. He trained his children to play their horns and instilled in them a profound sense of the deeply spiritual roots of the music. The Hypnotic Brass Ensembles music ranges from hypnotizing grooves to jazzy funk.

programme.title: Sven Hammond Soul
programme.sub-title: Sven Hammond Soul: Tivoli de Helling
programme.desc: Although its music might sound like the sound track of any 1970s American car chase movie, the band Sven Hammond Soul is from the Netherlands. This steaming soul machine is headed by Sven Figee, who prefers to attack rather than play his Hammond organ. In April 2012, the band was augmented with vocalist Jenny Lane. Todays recordings were made at a steaming live performance at Utrechts Tivoli in 2012.

programme.title: North Sea Jazz Classics
programme.desc: Registration of the performance of the Ahmad Jamal Trio at North Sea Jazz on July 16.

programme.title: Count Basie and his Orchestra live in Charleroi
programme.desc: Count Basie is one of the most important bandleaders of the swing era. With the exception of a brief period in the early 50s, he led a big band from 1935 until his death almost 50 years later. Basies orchestra was characterized by a light, swinging rhythm section that he led from the piano, lively ensemble work, and generous soloing. Basie was not a composer like Duke Ellington or an important soloist like Benny Goodman. His instrument was his band, which was considered the epitome of swing and deeply influenced jazz. In this 1961 concert recording, Count Basie takes the stage in Charleroi.

programme.title: Kurhaus Scheveningen
programme.desc: The Dutch world-class jazz pianist Peter Beets has shared the stage with jazz greats like Chick Corea, Wynton Marsalis, "Toots" Thielemans, Elvin Jones, George Coleman, Johnny Griffin, Benny Golson and John Clayton. From birth, Beets was surrounded by music: he heard classical music from his mother, who is a music pedagogue, and he heard jazz from his father, who has a great fan of Oscar Peterson and Art Blakey. Although Beets parents originally did not associate the word "musician" with the word "career", music is definitely in the familys blood. At this concert at the Kurhaus in Scheveningen, the Netherlands, Peter Beets teams up with the world-famous guitarist Kurt Rosenwinkel. With a career spanning almost twenty-five years and including collaborating with dynamic peers like Brad Mehldau, Brian Blade, Mark Turner, Joshua Redman, Chris Potter, as well as esteemed jazz legends like Joe Henderson, Paul Motian and Gary Burton, Rosenwinkels indelible mark in music is the consummation of being steeped in the rich and deep traditions of jazz, springing off of the shoulders of such vital underpinnings to elevate his own art to new heights, evolving the language in a way no other guitarist has since his arrival. This collaboration between Beets and Rosenwinkel guarantees brilliant music.

programme.title: Anita Oday Live in Sweden 1963
programme.desc: Anita ODay boasts two wonderful concerts from 1963 and 1970 that present the "jazz singer supreme" in impeccable form. ODays horn-based approach to singing is in full effect throughout both shows including stand-out renditions in each show of audience favorites "Tea For Two" and "Sweet Georgia Brown" (both reprised from her triumphant appearance at the 1958 Newport Jazz Festival.) This show is a fitting testimony to one of jazz musics true originals and shows unequivocally why she is ranked in the top tier of vocalists along with Ella Fitzgerald, Sarah Vaughan, and Billie Holiday.

programme.title: DJAZZ Clips
programme.desc: An extraordinary collection of clips in all jazz genres from the most beautiful concerts and the most special festivals, performed by the finest jazz musicians.

programme.title: Lex Jasper Trio
programme.sub-title: Lex Jasper Trio: Happy Days Are Here Again
programme.desc: Lex Jasper Trio: Happy Days Are Here Again - the title says is all… After an automobile accident and 15 years of revalidation, he is back! Together with his musical pals Edwin Corzilius (double bass) and Frits Landesbergen (drums), pianist and composer Lex Jasper celebrates his return to jazz club The Duke in the Dutch village of Nistelrode. Following his car accident, Lex nearly joined the leagues of Netherlands "forgotten" jazz heroes, though he is still considered one of the most important artists and composers of his generation and Dutch jazz history. Jasper played and recorded with all the greats, including Toots Thielemans, Clark Terry, Joe Pass, and Rita Reys.

programme.title: Les McCann
programme.sub-title: Les McCann: Live in New Orleans
programme.desc: Autodidact Les McCann became an international jazz star he is today after the release of his album "Swiss Movement" in 1968 which was recorded with Eddie Harris. However this musician has many other sides of achievements than that one record such as; McCann effortlessly switched between styles and stood his ground in every role from bop to fusion, from vocals to electric piano and clavinet to synthesizer, his is mix of church music and swing fits perfectly in the spirit of his time although at one point within the 90s he was only able to play with a single finger due to his illness. In todays broadcast, McCann brings gospel back to the New Orleans where this set was played in 1983. McCanns vocals triumph in the soulful performance of many of his hits, including Just Like Magic. He is accompanied by his fantastic "Magic Band" consisting of saxophonist Bobby Bryant Jr., bassist Curtis Roberson Jr. and drummer Tony St. James.

programme.title: John Coltrane
programme.desc: The mere mention of the name John Coltrane evokes a deeply emotional, often spiritual response from even the most casual jazz fan. Dexter Gordon was a fantastic saxophonist. Miles Davis was a genius. Coltrane stood above - he was a visionary, a saint-like figure. By the standards of most jazz musicians, his life was uneventful. Sure, he had a heroin habit for a while, and Miles Davis punched him, but once hed experienced the "spiritual awakening" described in the liner notes of his 1965 album A Love Supreme, he dedicated himself to his music with extreme single-mindedness. This broadcast of Coltranes 1965 performance at the short-lived Belgian jazz festival in Comblain-la-Tour features Tranes classic quartet with Elvin Jones (drums), Jimmy Garrison (bass) and McCoy Tyner (piano).

programme.title: DJAZZ Clips
programme.desc: An extraordinary collection of clips in all jazz genres from the most beautiful concerts and the most special festivals, performed by the finest jazz musicians.

programme.title: Jazz in Comblain-la-Tour, 1963
programme.desc: In 1963,small town in Belgium named; Comblain-la-Tour hosted an exciting line up of both new and old jazz groups. The British trombonist Charlie Galbraiths All Star Jazz Band performes classic Dixieland jazz. Next up is German singer Knut Kiesewetter who backs up from the Prague Dixieland Band, sings the blues. Perhaps the highlight of this event is the coupling of American alto saxophonist Bud Shank with Dutch pianist Pim Jacobs and his trio, whom play standards and bossa nova and the French clarinetist Marc Laferrière with his New Orleans Stompers combined with more classic Dixieland.

programme.title: Tribute to Django Reinhardt
programme.sub-title: Tribute to Django Reinhardt: Rosenberg meets Beets
programme.desc: Bireli Lagrène is a French jazz guitarist born on September 4, 1966 in a family of gypsy tradition. His brother and his father introduced him from an early age to the repertoire of Django Reinhardt, whose influence is still felt in the style of Lagrène. In this performance, Lagrène pays homage to Django Reinhardt with his son, Babik Reinhardt.

programme.title: Tribute to Monk
programme.desc: Jazz à Vienne is one of the worlds most prestigious jazz festivals. Ever since 1981, it has attracted a mix of jazz legends and exciting newcomers, with many of them playing return engagements. Each year welcomes outstanding international stars to the historical Le Theâtre Antique to impress and inspire their audiences. In 2017, French pianist Laurent de Wilde performed his tribute to jazz icon Thelonious Monk at Jazz à Vienne. Alongside bassist Jerôme Regard and drummer Donald Kontomanou, De Wilde gives a respectful and engaging homage built upon 20 years of study.

programme.title: Kultuuristuudio. Looming
programme.desc: "Kultuuristuudio. Looming" toob vaatajate ette režissoor Rasmus Merivoo 2006. aastal ulikooli lõputoona valminud filmi "Tulnukas ehk Valdise paasemine 11 osas" tagamaad. Saatejuht Meelis Oidsalu vaatab koos naitleja Indrek Ojari, psuhholoog Mati Heidmetsa ja kultuuriloolase Marju Kõivupuuga filmis ohtralt kasutatud vagisõnade taha: mis neid ropendada ja kakelda armastavaid tuupe kaivitab ning mida on sel tanastegi teismeliste lemmikuks olevas filmis uldse kultuurset?

programme.title: Lainud on jaanud
programme.desc: New Delhis sundinud režissoor Varun Trikha randas aastaid kaameraga Setomaal, et jaadvustada sealsete inimeste lugusid ning nende suhestumist mineviku ja olevikuga. Riigipiiride tõttu lõhkikistud ajalooline Petserimaa on paik, mis paneb mõtisklema kaotusest, eraldusest, lahkumissunnist ning soovist oma kultuuriga taas uhendust leida. Kuue aasta valtel tõmbab Varun Trikhat ikka ja jalle tagasi kolme kohaliku asuka juurde, kes on otsustanud jaada sellele eikellegimaale. Nad ullatavad teda lugudega oma unenagudest, mis moodunut ja poordumatult kaotatut leevendavad. Omaparasel moel aratavad need lood ules ka režissoori enda malestused ja otsingud. Ühel ool, huljatud majas peavarju leidnuna, naeb ta salaparast und oma ammulahkunud vanaisast, keda ta pole kunagi kohanud, ning ta otsustab valja selgitada, kes tema vanaisa tegelikult oli. Oma poeetilises, visuaalselt ja tahenduskihtidelt rikkas filmis paotab Varun Trikha unenaolise ukse korraga nii Eesti kui ka India uhiskonna haavadesse ning oma isiklikku perekonnalukku.

programme.title: Madal haud
programme.desc: R: Danny Boyle. O: Ewan McGregor, Christopher Eccleston. Kolm sõpra avastavad, et nende uus korterikaaslane on mustilisel kombel surnud ja maha jatnud kohvritaie raha. Meeleheitlikult laibale sobivat asukohta otsides hakkavad sõprade vahele tekkima esimesed hõõrdumised, mis viivad ootamatute tagajargedeni. Hinnatud lavastaja Danny Boylei ("Rentslimiljonar", "127 tundi") debuutmangufilm andis uue hingamise moodunud sajandi lõpuaastate inglise krimikomoodia žanrile, mida iseloomustas cooli valjapeetusega ehtbritilik musta huumoriga vurtsitatud stiil. Filmi edust said karjaaris tuule tiibadesse nii lavastaja Boyle, stsenaariumi autor John Hodges kui ka noor naitleja Ewan McGregor, kes kõik koos seisid ka 1996. aastal kinosid tormtulena vallutanud filmi "Trainspotting" tegemise taga.

Bailey (haale annab taas Josh Gad, "Lumekuninganna ja igavene talv", "Jobs") elab mõnusalt Michigani farmis oma "poisi" Ethani (Dennis Quaid, "Koera elu mõte", "Paev parast homset") ja Ethani naise Hannahga (Marg Helgenberger telesarjast "CSI: kriminalistid"). Kui Bailey hing valmistub sellest elust jargmisesse liikuma, lubab ta Ethanile CJ ules otsida ja teda iga hinna eest kaitsta. Nii algabki Bailey seiklus labi mitme elu, mida taidavad armastus, sõprus ja puhendumus. Tema, CJ ja CJ parim sõber Trent puutuvad kokku rõõmu ja sudame murdumisega, muusika ja naeruga, ja mõne eriti hea kõhusugamisega.

programme.title: Kena vaikne kohake 2
programme.desc: John Krasinski lavastatud õudus-thrilleri "Kena vaikne kohake" teine peatukk jalgib Abbottite perekonna saatust parast esimeses osas aset leidnud traagilisi sundmusi ning heidab pilgu ka võõrolendite saabumise hetke. Parast pereisa Lee (John Krasinski) eneseohverdust, et paasta oma laste elu, on ema Evelyn (Emily Blunt) sunnitud nende senise kodu maha jatma. Pere asub teele, et leida ellujaanuid, kellega võiks jõud uhendada. Kuid peagi selgub, et heli abil jahti pidavad võikad elukad pole ainsad, kes liivaribalt kõrvale astudes su elu kallale kipuvad.

programme.title: Kodachrome - Elu pildid
programme.desc: Plaadikompanii veteran Matt Ryder (Jason Sudeikis) võtab ette pika autosõidu oma vana ja haige isa Benjaminiga (Ed Harris), sihiks viimane labor maailmas, kus ilmutatakse Kodachrome filmi. Benjamin Ryder on nimelt endine tippfotograaf ja tahab teada, mis on jaadvustatud neljale vanale filmirullile, mille ta oma asjade seast leidis. Kahe nageleva mehega sõidab kaasa Beni põetaja Zooey (Elizabeth Olsen). Kõik kolm puuavad hakkama saada poordumatult muutuvas maailmas, uritades oma minevikku selja taha jatta. Huumoriga vurtsitatud draama "Kodachrome _ elu pildid" raagib tegemata valikutest, valusatest-ilusatest malestustest ja andestuse võimalikkusest. Osades Ed Harris ("Westworld", "Apollo 13"), Jason Sudeikis ("Vastikud ulemused"), Elizabeth Olsen ("Tasujad: Igaviku sõda", "Wind River"), Bruce Greenwood ("Kingsman: Kuldne ring", "Geralds Game") ja Dennis Haysbert ("24"). Filmi lavastas Mark Raso ("Copenhagen"), stsenaariumi kirjutas Jonathan Tropper ("This Is Where I Leave You", "Banshee") A.G. Sulzbergeri artikli ainetel.

programme.title: Mina, Tonya
programme.desc: Tonya Harding laks USA ajalukku kui kuulsaim ja skandaalseim iluuisutaja. Tema meisterlikkus leidis pidevalt kinnitust, kuid alatiste skandaalide tõttu oli ta kogu aeg kollases ajakirjanduses.

programme.title: Elliot, kõige vaiksem põhjapõder
programme.desc: Animafilmi tele-esilinastus! Saage tuttavaks tillukese hobusega, kel on hiigelsuur suda ja kes kannab nime Elliot. Üks Jõuluvana põhjapõtradest teatab 21. detsembril ootamatult, et kavatseb pensionile jaada. Talle on vaja leida asendaja ning sellega on kiire! Sudamlik suksu Elliot ja tema parim sõber võtavad suuna Põhjanabale, et võtta osa põhjapõtrade katsetest. Elliot soovib naidata, et just tema on vabaks jaanud ametikohale kõige sobivam... hobune!? Sest suured unistajad unistavadki ju suurelt. Lõbusas ja lustakas jõuluseikluses annavad tegelaskujudele oma haaled teiste seas Tarvo Krall, Erki Aule, Piret Simson, Kati Ong, Karin Aule, Rauno Kaibiainen ja Maarius Parn.

programme.title: Rikkis Ron
programme.desc: Vaimuka animaseikluse "Rikkis Ron" peategelasteks on Barney, ebapopulaarne keskkooliõpilane, ning Ron, tema uhiuus digitaalselt uhendatud, kõndiv ja kõnelev nutiseade, mis peaks olema automaatselt tema parim sõber.

programme.title: Harakapoeg Pingviin
programme.desc: Tõestisundinud lool põhinev film jutustab noorest pereemast nimega Sam Bloom (Naomi Watts), kelle maailm pooratakse pea peale paeval, kui naine õnnetu kukkumise jarel halvatuks jaab. Sami armastav abikaasa Cameron (Andrew Lincoln), tema kolm poega ning ema (Jackie Weaver) naevad tublisti vaeva, et kohaneda uue olukorraga. Pinged koduseinte vahel kasvavad, kuni pere saab ootamatu abilise: vigastatud harakapoja, kellele pannakse nimeks... Pingviin. Linnu saabumine pakub teretulnud vaheldust ning toob kõige suurema muutuse just paljukannatanud Sami jaoks, õpetades teda tasapisi uuesti elama.

programme.title: Baleriin
programme.desc: USA 2017 animatsioon Lavastaja: Eric Summer, Eric Warin Osades: Mirtel Pohla, Mart Muurisepp, Mart Pius, Eduard Toman,Age Oks jt. Felicie on Bretagneist parit noor orb, kel on vaid uks kirg - tantsimine. Ühes parima sõbra Victoriga, kes ihkab suureks leiutajaks saada, kavandab ta poorase põgenemise orbudekodust Valguse linna Pariisi, kus Eiffeli torni alles ehitatakse! Felicie peab nagema vaeva, nagu ei iial varem, end uletama ja õppima vigadest, kui tahab teha teoks oma metsikuima unistuse ja saada Pariisi ooperiteatris priimabaleriiniks.

programme.title: Bill ja Ted
programme.desc: William "Bill" S. Preston Esq. ja Theodore "Ted" Logani jaoks on seekordsel ajarannul kaalul rohkem kui eal varem. Nuudseks keskealised parimad sõbrad asuvad oma rocknrolli saatuse taide viimiseks uuele seiklusele, kui kulaline tulevikust teatab, et vaid nende laul saab paasta maailma. Neid aitavad nende tutred, ajaloolised tegelased ja muusikalegendid, et leida laulu, mis muudaks maailma õigeks ja tooks universumisse harmooniat.

programme.title: Oihhh! Seiklus jatkub
programme.desc: Kui nii edasi laheb, on lõpp kaes! 147 paeva laevas ilma maitsva liha, leiva ja magustoiduta! Ümberringi ainult meri, ei mingit maad silmapiiril, laeval aga 50 tuhat erinevat ja vaga naljast looma, lindu ja kaks sinna juhuslikult sattunud pesalooma. Aga see pole veel kõige hirmsam. Hirmus on see, et varsti saab otsa isegi too jube roheline puder. Ja siis … Siis ei hooli enam keegi reeglist "sina ei pea mitte teist elajat ara sooma"! Kaotanud igasuguse lootuse, laseb kuningas lõvi taevasse tuvi, et see lendaks kõrgele ja otsiks maad … Aga maa leiavad hoopis taiesti juhuslikult laevast valja pudenenud paharetid – grump Liia ja pesaloom Finny! Torm heidab nad erakordselt kaunile saarele.

programme.title: Jargmine ring
programme.desc: Ajaloo, psuhholoogia, muusika ja kehalise õpetaja kontrollivad teaduslikku teooriat, et inimeste kannatusi põhjustab ebapiisavalt alkoholi hulk veres ja et õnnelik olemiseks peab olema pisut svipsis.

programme.title: Mortdecai
programme.desc: Rabeledes vihaste venelaste, Briti salaagentide, oma ilmatu pikkade jalgadega naise ja rahvusvahelise terroristi vahel, peab elurõõmus kunstikaupmees ja poole kohaga suli Charlie Mortdecai, relvaks ainult oma hea valimus ja eriline sarm, minema teisele poole maakera, et tagasi saada varastatud maal, mis kuulujuttude põhjal peidab endas koodi natside kullaga taidetud salajasele pangakontole.

programme.title: La La Land
programme.desc: Algajast naitlejanna Mias ja puhendunud džassmuusik Sebastian naevad vaeva, et saada hakkama linnas, mis on kuulus lootuste purustamise ja sudamete murdmise poolest. See tanapaeva Los Angeleses aset leidev ja igapaevaelust pajatav originaalmuusikal vaatleb rõõmu ja valu, mis oma unistuste poole puudlemisega kaasas kaivad. Film kandideeris 14 Oscarile.

programme.title: Huppaja
programme.desc: Tavaline nooruk avastab, et tal on ebatavaline võime liikuda hetkega mistahes maakera paika. Olles uue võimega kohanenud, avastab ta, et talle peetakse jahti.

programme.title: Geenius ja hullumeelne
programme.desc: 19. sajandi Inglismaal tootab Oxfordi professor ajaloo esimese inglise keele sõnaraamatu kallal. Ta kasutab oma toos hullumajja lukustatud Yalei kolleegi abi.

programme.title: Saag X
programme.desc: John Kramer (Tobin Bell) on tagasi. Filmisarja "Saag" seni kõige hairivam osa raagib Jigsaw kõige isiklikumast mangust. Sundmused leiavad aset filmide "Saag" ja "Saag II" vahel, kui haige ja meeleheitel John reisib Mehhikosse riskantse ja eksperimentaalse meditsiinilise protseduuri jaoks, lootuses leida imeravim oma vahile. Ta avastab, et see kõik on pettus kõige haavatavamate inimeste tussamiseks. Kurikuulus sarimõrvar leiab uue eesmargi ja asub taas toole, poorates olukorra petturite jaoks umber. Ta teeb seda endale omasel viisil, salakavalate, hullumeelsete ja leidlike lõksude abil.

programme.title: Saatuse iroonia Ameerika moodi
programme.desc: USA 2022 romantiline komoodia Lavastaja:Marius Vaisberg Osades:Emma Roberts, Thomas Mann Margot ja Griffin usuvad mõlemad armastusse, aga pole kunagi jõudnud selle tõelise tahenduseni. Kumbki ei tea teise olemasolust, kuni uhel tormisel uusaastaool viib saatus nad kokku. Tulemuseks tõeline aparduste rada, koomiline kaos, millesse sukeldudes võivad noored saada rohkem, kui oleks arvatagi osanud.

programme.desc: Noor lavastaja valib Broadway uude tantsulavastusse kaasaegse tantsija ja uuendusmeelse pianisti. Peagi avastavad noored end armukolmnurgast, mis kruvib pinged lakke ja kõigil tuleb halastamatus võitluses selle eest lõivu maksta.

programme.desc: Tempoka ja sudantsoojendava komoodia naol on tegemist Robert Zemeckise populaarse 1980-ndate klassikaga.

programme.desc: Ambitsioonikas noor jazz-trummar Andrew Neyman õpib mainekas konservatooriumis janunedes olla parimatest parim. Terence Fletcher on pedagoog, kes on tuntud nii oma akadeemilise võimekuse kui ka kusitavalt tooreste meetodite poolest.

programme.title: Lahingud ladude parast
programme.desc: Ostjad suunduvad Comptonisse, kus Jarrod saab endale uue huudnime ja leiab midagi, mida ta kunagi kogus. Mike ostab lao, mida Herb ei taha ja Barry uhineb oma vana sõbra Kennyga.

programme.title: William Shatneriga seletamatutes paikades
programme.desc: Kõige suurem mõistatus, millele puudub seni vastus, võib olla meie saatus parast surma. Ehk annavad vihjeid ebaharilikud surmalahedased juhtumid.

programme.title: Pandikunnid
programme.desc: Rick uritab New Yorgis teha tehingu haruldase tehnikavidina ostmiseks. Kas see magus tukk suudab Ricki ahvatleda või loobub ta sellest? Poodi jõuab muuja Stan Lee Funko Popi erivaljaandega. Kas Corey teeb supertehingu?

programme.title: Oak Islandi needus
programme.desc: Samal ajal, kui tõendid portugallaste iidse kohaloleku kohta kuhjuvad, võib sugavalt soost leitud salaparane artefakt meile oelda, et Fred Nolani pool sajandit tagasi esitatud teooria võib olla õige.

programme.title: Iidsed tulnukad
programme.desc: Rohkem kui 50 riigis on dokumenteeritud ule 10 000 viljaringi moodustise, millest paljudel on omadusi, mis ei allu tavaparastele seletustele. Kas need on maavalise paritoluga? Ja kui jah, siis mis on nende eesmark?

programme.title: Suurimad roovid Pierce Brosnaniga
programme.desc: Itaalia varaste eliitgrupp võtab sihikule Antwerpeni Maailma Teemandikeskuse varakambri. Parast 27 kuud kestnud planeerimist viivad nad oma keerulise plaani ellu ja roovivad enam kui 100 miljonit dollarit.

programme.title: Uskumatu koos Dan Aykroydiga
programme.desc: Laeva- ja lennuõnnetused, kadumised ja UFO-de nagemised - mida kõike veel! Selles osas uuritakse Michigani jarve kolmnurka ja teisi metsikuid ja kummalisi kohti, sealhulgas hirmsat nukke tais saart ja koopaid, mis varjavad surmavaid viiruseid.

programme.title: Oksjonikutid
programme.desc: Pandipoe ajalooga Ton ja Allen alustavad oma karjaari jargmist peatukki suure pauguga. Nad avastavad teise maailmasõja aegse tulirelva ja vene kosmonautide skafandri, mis võib olla nende seni suurim leid... kui see on tõeline.

programme.title: Oksjonikutid
programme.desc: Ton ja Allen lahevad vastamisi oma endise assistendi Carolyniga, samal ajal kui Ton võitleb seljavaluga. Mehed avastavad automaat-õhupussi ja kui labiraakimised trikirambi muumiseks lahevad halvasti, seisab Allen raske otsuse ees.

programme.title: Oksjonikutid
programme.desc: Viimase hetke oksjon Norwalkis osutub keeruliseks, kui Ton ja Allen lahevad vastamisi tõelise kauboipaariga. Kui tolm settib, avastavad poisid 3D-printeri ja haardekonksuga relva, millest tulistamist ei jõua nad ara oodata.

programme.title: Pandikunnid
programme.desc: Rick Harrison koos oma perega on Las Vegases asuva pandimaja omanikud. Sari "Pandikunnid" jalgib mida põnevat pandimajja tuuakse ning mida muuakse. Kaib pidev tingimine hindade ule ning aeg-ajalt satub pandimajja ka vaga vaartuslikke esemeid.

programme.title: Pandikunnid
programme.desc: Rick naeb punast varvi, kui poodi jõuab Rolex Submariner. Kas tema pakkumine loob laineid või on see lihtsalt ajaraiskamine? Ja hiljem uritab Rick mitte plahvatada rõõmust, kui suundub ule vaatama Boliivia aikesetopside komplekti.

programme.title: Oak Islandi needus
programme.desc: Mis peitub Oak Islandi all? Keegi ei tea seda, ja igauks, kes on puudnud seda valja selgitada, on kokku puutunud ootamatu probleemiga - lõksudega. Saabuvad Lagina vennad Michiganist. Sel suvel hakkavad nad kaevama ja rakendavad uudset tehnoloogiat.

programme.title: Iidsed tulnukad
programme.desc: Põhja-Ameerika põlisrahvaste traditsioonides leidub lugusid tahe-eellastest: võimsatest olenditest, kes laskusid Maale kauges minevikus ja on mõnikord ka tanapaeval kohal.

programme.title: Lahingud ladude parast
programme.desc: Ivy veab Isaiah Victorvillei karistuseks, et ta on saanud hindeks kolmesid. Kenny tahab sisustada oma uut maja, kuid tema teel on kaheksa põhjust. Ja me ei taha kõlada imalalt, aga Lisa õpib palju.

programme.title: Lahingud ladude parast
programme.desc: Lisa paneb selga oma kauboivarustuse, Rene võtab ette tagasihoidliku laoboksi ja Brandi laheb ruustama. Ivy ja tema poisid saavad aimu pensionaride elust ja Darrell ei tunne end sugugi iseendana.

programme.title: Lahingud ladude parast
programme.desc: Rene ja Casey võtavad San Bernardinos riski ja Kenny komistab mõne kummalise valimusega autoosa otsa. Vahepeal hoiab Lisa katastroofi eemal ebatavaliselt kalli kapi abil.

programme.title: Iidsed tulnukad
programme.desc: Piki maakera põhjapoolkera 37. laiuskraadi on olnud nii palju teateid UFOde ja muude salaparaste sundmuste kohta, et seda on nimetatud UFO-de superkiirteeks. Kas sellel laiuskraadil võib olla midagi, mis meelitab maavaliseid kulastajaid?

programme.title: William Shatneriga seletamatutes paikades

programme.title: Iidsed tulnukad

programme.title: Lahingud ladude parast
programme.desc: Ostjad suunduvad Homelandi, aga Harrise vennad oleksid pidanud koju jaama. Jarrod ja Brandi tegelevad ostmisega, pinged samas kasvavad. Rene ja Casey ostavad lao, aga saavad peagi aru, et on teinud vea.

programme.title: Lahingud ladude parast
programme.desc: Jarrod ja Brandi leiavad ebatavalise kunstiteose, Rene ja Casey naudivad veini ning Barry raamatupidaja uritab teda tagasi hoida.

programme.title: William Shatneriga seletamatutes paikades
programme.desc: Ka parast sajandeid kestnud uurimist on inimmõistus endiselt suureks saladuseks. Kas kõige olulisem inimmasin - aju, võib-olla veel võimsam, kui me ette kujutame?

programme.title: Pandikunnid
programme.desc: Kas Chum laseb oma hambad kaiku, kui siseneb klient "Elavate surnute" naitlejate autogrammidega kujukeste kollektsiooniga? Corey tunneb end hasti, kui pandimajja ilmub Rock n Roll High Schooli plakat. Kas tehing on muusika tema kõrvadele?

programme.title: Oak Islandi needus
programme.desc: Mis peitub Oak Islandi all? Keegi ei tea seda, ja igauks, kes on puudnud seda valja selgitada, on kokku puutunud ootamatu probleemiga - lõksudega. Saabuvad Lagina vennad Michiganist. Sel suvel hakkavad nad kaevama ja rakendavad uudset tehnoloogiat.

programme.title: Warriors
programme.desc: Travel the globe alongside modern-day warrior, Terry Schappert, and go inside the culture of some of the most famous warriors of all time to explore their weaponry, tactics and, ultimately, their psyche.

programme.title: Buried
programme.desc: Seven years after the alleged end of the Templars, signs they were rising again appear in Portugal. The team investigate a plan to restart the Templars and explore possibilities that the "Templars 2.0" quietly consolidate power around the world.

programme.title: Monsterquest
programme.desc: In the fall of 1952, witnesses in Flatwoods, West Virginia, reportedly encountered a creature with reptilian skin in a strange craft. As sightings continue, MonsterQuest attempts to uncover the beast that has terrorised this town for sixty years.

programme.title: Lost Worlds
programme.desc: Documentary series that brings back to life lost cities, structures, cultures, and civilisations, transporting viewers back in time and revealing the truth behind some of historys most iconic eras. Using a combination of cutting-edge technology and archaeological research, the team detail what life was like for these places during their peak of their powers, and use visual overlays to compare past and present landscapes.

programme.title: Evolve
programme.desc: Documentary series. Evolve takes an in-depth look at the evolution of some of the planets most iconic animals. Using computer generated imagery and experimental science, the team take you on a journey through history to look at how these species evolved to fit their habitats and surroundings. The show explores the diverse and unique anatomy changes our planets historic species have gone through.

programme.title: Iidsed tulnukad
programme.desc: Muistsete aegade imperaatoritele, kuningatele ja vaaraodele omistati sageli uleloomulikku jõudu, võimeid ja tarkust, alamad pidasid neid sageli jumalateks. Kes need erakordsed juhid tegelikult olid?

programme.title: How the Earth was made
programme.desc: With the help of expert geologists and various scientists, How the Earth Was Made is a remarkable documentary series that examines the powerful forces and events that have shaped our planet. Using stunning, computer generated cinematography, viewers are transported back billions of years to learn how our planet was formed, and the drastically different changes it has witnessed.

programme.title: UFO Hunters
programme.desc: American docuseries following William J. Birnes and his team of "ufologists" as they search for evidence of extra-terrestrial life. Listen to witness accounts of shocking close encounters, and join the team as they analyse photographic and video evidence in search of the truth. As they look into some of the most notorious alien hot-spots in the US, is space is really as empty as we think?

programme.title: The Who
programme.sub-title: The Who: Live At the Isle Of Wight Festival
programme.desc: In 2004 The Who returned to the Isle Of Wight Festival for the first time since their legendary performance in 1970. After a long absence, the festival had been reborn in 2002 and continues to this day. Their UK concerts in 2004 were the first in their home country since the death of founder member John Entwistle. As the evening shadows lengthened across the festival site, The Who took to the stage and delivered an incendiary performance packed with hit singles and classic album tracks and the concert more than lived up to the fans expectations and memories of 1970.

programme.title: Alice in Chains - Unplugged
programme.desc: In their first live concert in over 2 years (and possibly their last concert ever), Alternative/metal group Alice in Chains performs acoustically at MTV Unplugged. Includes acoustic versions of the hit songs ""Got Me Wrong,"" ""Rooster,"" ""Would?,"" and ""Down in a Hole.

programme.title: Robbie Williams - Live at the Apple Music Festival
programme.desc: A brand new show that brings a veteran artist at his best! The talented artist, who became famous in the group ""Take That"", lacks presentations, but he himself begins his show by saying: ""Let me resubmit ..."". Robbie Williams has the ability to reinvent himself, exhibiting so much energy that he seems to be a rookie artist. Already in the 40s band of pop music, Robbie is more than an artist consecrated worldwide, is a reference with hits present in the best lists of consecrated DJs. This show at the Roundhouse coincided with the announcement of their 11th solo album, Heavy Entertainment Show, just released. The new albums title reflects Williams performance as energy-dense as his 11-member big band, including his hits partner Guy Chambers on the piano. A formidable 90 minute pop odyssey. Mixing tracks from his Take That era, old or new, his songs allow him to reclaim his throne from an artist who dominates the stage - in fact, there is no one in pop music who combines his monumental energy with music Touching. A magical moment can be perceived in ""A Better Man"", only with the guitar on stage; Proof that he is an artist that goes beyond the scenery. This Blu-Ray shows the trajectory of an artist who knows how to renew himself every lap; An example for the new generations of music that are lost in appearance, forgetting the essential aspect that Robbie Williams is revealing more and more.

programme.title: Snow Patrol - Live At Somerset House
programme.desc: With their third album, Final Straw, selling a cool 1.5 million in the UK in its year of release, Snow Patrols reputation as a remarkable band remains intact. "Live At Somerset House" reveals why the band is praised for delivering fantastic live performances. It also places them at one of Londons most gorgeous settings which complements the bands distinctive and provocative sound perfectly. Performing live for the first time with a string section, this amazing Snow Patrol concert, features all the key hits including Run, Spitting Games, "Chocolate" and a blistering version of Tiny Little Fractures.

programme.title: The day the Rock Star Died
programme.desc: Michael Jackson American singer, songwriter, dancer and simply the King of Pop. His contributions to music, dance, and publicized personal life made him a global figure in popular culture for over four decades. Jackson made his professional debut in 1964 as a member of The Jackson 5, soon becoming a dominant figure in popular music. His music videos, "Beat It"", "Billie Jean"", and "Thriller"" are credited with breaking racism in the USA and transforming the medium into an art form. Thriller is the best-selling album of all time. Jackson was the most awarded recording artist in the history of popular music. Aspects of Jacksons personal life generated controversy and while preparing for his comeback concert series, This Is It, Jackson died of acute Propofol and Benzodiazepine intoxication on June 25, 2009, after suffering from cardiac arrest. The Los Angeles County Department of Medical Examiner Coroner ruled his death a homicide, and his personal physician, Conrad Murray.

programme.title: Bastille - Reading and Leeds Festival
programme.desc: The Reading and Leeds Festivals are a pair of annual music festivals that take place in Reading and Leeds, England. The events both happen on the bank holiday weekend in August (on Friday, Saturday, Sunday), and share the same bill (occasionally with one or two exceptions). The festivals origins date to the Beaulieu Jazz Festival (1956-1961) which became the National Jazz Festival in 1961 (The National Jazz and Blues Festival in 1963) and settled in Reading in 1971. In 1999 a second leg was added at Leeds. Featuring : Bastille.

programme.desc: In 2004 The Who returned to the Isle Of Wight Festival for the first time since their legendary performance in 1970. After a long absence, the festival had been reborn in 2002 and continues to this day. Their UK concerts in 2004 were the first in their home country since the death of founder member John Entwistle. As the evening shadows lengthened across the festival site, The Who took to the stage and delivered an incendiary performance packed with hit singles and classic album tracks and the concert more than lived up to the fans expectations and memories of 1970.

programme.title: Snow Patrol - Live At Somerset House

"Live At Somerset House" reveals why the band is praised for delivering fantastic live performances. It also places them at one of Londons most gorgeous settings which complements the bands distinctive and provocative sound perfectly. Performing live for the first time with a string section, this amazing Snow Patrol concert, features all the key hits including Run, Spitting Games, "Chocolate" and a blistering version of Tiny Little Fractures.

programme.title: The day the Rock Star Died
programme.desc: Janis Joplin was one of the most successful and widely-known female rock stars of her era. After releasing three albums, she died of a heroin overdose at the age of 27. Her fourth album, Pearl, was released in January 1971, just over three months after her death. It reached number one on the Billboard charts. Her Legacy. The big-voiced, bluesy singer dominated the stage, forged her own path and paved the way for the female singers who followed.

programme.desc: Reisisellid Rait ja onu Raiu on sõitnud juba teiselepoole Venemaad ning nuud saab ka maantee otsa. Talveteedel saavad mehed tunda tõelist karget Siberit, temperatuur langeb -53 kraadini ning uhele autole on see liig mis liig, kuid karm Siber sellega ei piirdu.

programme.title: Reis Venemaa lõppu _ Tśukotka
programme.desc: Reisisellid Rait ja onu Raiu kohtavad lõbusat tšuki harrat, kes teab Eestit vaga hasti. Loodus on lummavalt kaunis ning keset tundrat võib leida ka kulmunud kalu, millest suppi keeta. Peagi satutakse tsooni, kus mehed olla ei tohiks.

programme.title: CSI Kriminalistid
programme.desc: Kui CSI jõuab miniatuuridega seotud tapja tabamisele lahemale kui iial varem, laheb Sara kaduma. Tema suhe Grissomiga tuleb avalikuks.

programme.title: Haneema
programme.desc: Emil survestab Sonjat, kuna sadamast leiti midagi ootamatut. Anders vabastatakse jalamonitoriga. Nina saab ootamatut abi ja Lukas teeb tahtsa otsuse.

programme.title: Masterchef Soome
programme.desc: Võistlejad seisavad rohelise urdilaua ees ja õigete urtide aratundmise korral on neil võimalus valtida pingeulesannet, mille kaigus tuleb valmistada magustoit. Ühel võistlejal tuleb koogist lahkuda.

programme.title: Schitts Creek
programme.desc: Kui Johnny oma suurt võitu tahistab, kuuleb Moira ootamatuid uudiseid, mis nende plaane muudavad. David teeb otsuse selle kohta, kus ta elada tahab, ja see tuleb perele ullatusena. Alexis ja Twyla vahetavad emotsionaalselt kingitusi.

programme.title: Schitts Creek
programme.desc: David on oma pulmapaeval vihma tõttu stressis, seega korraldab Patrick Davidile massaaži, et aidata tal lõõgastuda. Vahepeal puuab Johnny leida uut urituse toimumiskohta, Alexisel on piinlik oma riideaparduse tõttu ja Moira võtab endale pulmatseremoonia juhataja rolli.

programme.title: Milderid Marokos
programme.desc: Poorase reisiseikluse "Milderid Marokos" viimases osas liiguvad Piret, Egert, Milli ja Max tagasi Atlandi ookeani aarde. Seal kulastatakse erinevaid rannikukulakesi, antakse ulevaade Maroko supermarketite kõige põnevamatest toodetest ja musitseeritakse kohaliku gnawa-ansambliga.

programme.title: Sinine ingel
programme.desc: Sari "Sinine ingel" on varvikas pilt õitsenguaegadest 1980ndate aastate Helsingis, kus raha kasvab puude otsas, kabriolettide kiiremad kaigud panevad adrenaliini voolama ja solaarium on uus paike.

programme.title: CSI Kriminalistid
programme.desc: CSI - eliit mõrvauurimise ruhm. Neile ei jaa ukski kuritegu ega mõrv lahendamata. Piisab vaid uhest sõrmejaljest, juuksekarvast või kuuliaugust ja mõrvar võib kindel olla, et ta tabatakse.

programme.title: Metoodiline hullumine
programme.desc: Jason Mewes asub kasutama metoodilist naitlemist, et Hollywoodis suuremat tunnustust leida, kuid hakkab aeglaselt hulluma.

programme.title: Üksildased hinged
programme.desc: Musta huumoriga vurtsitatud (eba)romantiline komoodia. Mandy (Billie Piper, "I Hate Suzie") on oma eluga parajasse ummikusse jooksnud. Ta on kaasaegne naine. Ta on ema. Ta elab siiani ule oma vanemate keerukaid omavahelisi suhteid. Ja ta on kirjanik. Kui Mandy kohtub traditsiooniliste vaartushinnangutega Peteiga (Leo Bill, "28 paeva hiljem"), tekib nende vahel vagagi ebatraditsiooniline armusuhe…

programme.title: Suured keskvaksalid
programme.desc: Bahnhofstrasse tanava lõpus tervitavad teid aukartustaratav neorenessanslik paekivifassaad ning hoone rikkalikult kaunistatud saalid, salongid ja restoranid. Kilpkonnakilbi põhja tooni fassaadi tipus on Helvetia, Konfoderatsiooni naisallegooria. Ajalooline jaam kehastab koos oma neoklassitsistlike tornidega Šveitsi industriaalajastu õitsengut, mil toimus raudtee plahvatuslik areng. Tanapaeval peidab Zurichi HB jaam oma funktsioone hasti - marmorpõranda all peitub ulimodernne installatsioon, erinevate transpordiliikide vahelise koostoime mudel: kiirrongid, trammid, piirkondlikud kiirteed, jalgrattad... Jaam ise on transpordisõlm, milles raudteed on kolmel tasandil labi põimunud, ning mida labib iga paev pea 500 000 reisijat.

programme.title: CSI Kriminalistid
programme.desc: CSI - eliit mõrvauurimise ruhm. Neile ei jaa ukski kuritegu ega mõrv lahendamata. Piisab vaid uhest sõrmejaljest, juuksekarvast või kuuliaugust ja mõrvar võib kindel olla, et ta tabatakse.

programme.title: Haneema
programme.desc: Sonja vabastatakse ja ta naaseb poegade juurde. Malestusteenistusele ilmub soovimatu kulaline. Narkoparun Pinto Rosales esitab ultimaatumi. Sonja asub Östlingi-vastases sõjas runnakule.

programme.title: Masterchef Soome
programme.desc: Võistlejad hakkavad hotelli Scandic Grand Central koogis võistkondadena omavahel mõõdu võtma. Kumma meeskonna hommikusoogikandik aratab Masterchefi kohtunikes huvi?

programme.title: Mees teab
programme.desc: Pereisa Adam on sunnitud lastega rohkem aega veetma, kui tema abikaasa Andi otsustab taas toole naasta.

programme.title: Mees teab
programme.desc: Adami klient kingib talle kaks piletit Pittsburgh Steelersi mangule ning mees seisab raske valiku ees, kas võtta endaga kaasa Andi või Don.

programme.title: Rahast tehtud koos Brian Coxiga
programme.desc: Saade vaatleb Brianit teekonnal, millel mees uurib inimeste keerukat suhet raha ja jõukusega. Saate valtel raagib mees ka omaenda lugu, alates vaesuses uleskasvamisest kuni Hollywoodi kõrgepalgaliseks naitlejaks saamiseni, kus ta kehastab uht televisiooni rikkaimat ja verejanulisimat kapitalisti. Sari on Briani missioon kõrvaldada oma hirm vaesuse ees ning lahendada raha ja õnne keeruline kusimus. Terava huumori ja kartmatu uudishimuga Brian kaarib kaised ules Bronxi supikoogis, vestleb supermodellidega Miami Beachis, kohtub kodututega Harlemis ning kulastab Londoni kõige kallimas majas uht miljardari.

programme.title: CSI Kriminalistid
programme.desc: CSI - eliit mõrvauurimise ruhm. Neile ei jaa ukski kuritegu ega mõrv lahendamata. Piisab vaid uhest sõrmejaljest, juuksekarvast või kuuliaugust ja mõrvar võib kindel olla, et ta tabatakse.

programme.title: Rahu šokolaadi abil
programme.desc: Sudamlik draamakomoodia. Parast seda, kui tema perekonnale kuuluvat šokolaaditehast tabas pommirahe, puuab noor Suuria põgenik alustada uut elu Kanada vaikelinnas. Ta tahaks hakata arstiteadust õppima, ent avab isa nõudmisel siiski šokolaadiari, mis osutub vaga menukaks. Kuid noormehe hinges on siiski lõhe: kas valida omaenda kutsumus või taita muudkui isa soove. Tekkiv pinge avardab perekonna lõhki rebida… Film põhineb tõestisundinud lool.

programme.title: Parfuumid
programme.desc: Annei too on tema kirg ja kogu tema elu mõte, ta valmistab nimelt parfuume. Tal on erakordne anne - tundlik haistmismeel ja taielik puhendumus. Nagu aga sageli ikka, on liigselt toole keskendunud ja mingil alal vaga andekad loojad inimestena mitte nii kerged isiksused... Kui Anne palkab endale autojuhi, muutub tema elus palju. Lihtsast mehest, autojuht Guillaumeist saab naisele võrdne vastane, kellega koos saavad nii mõnedki elutõed selgemaks. Tegemist on sudantsoojendava linalooga sõprusest, toost ja elust.

programme.title: Tipptund
programme.desc: Tempokas põnevuskomoodia inspektor Leest (Jackie Chan), kel tuleb kurikaelte kaest paasta Hiina konsuli tutar. FBI pole aga uhegi valismaalase sekkumisest huvitatud ja nii saadetakse Leele vastu kõige araarvamatum detektiiv James Carter (Chris Tucker), et see võõrast saatkonnale ligi ei laseks. Carter otsustab aga hoopis koos Leega roovlid kinni nabida.

programme.title: Valelikud võrgutajad
programme.desc: Valelikud võrgutajad soostavad Hannat Über A kuusist paastma. Ainus moodus selleks on paljastada, kes mõrvas Charlotte DiLauretise.

programme.title: Surematu
programme.desc: Ciro on kurikuulus Napoli gangster, kelle tee viib Latti illegaalset ari ules ehitama. Parast kohtumist oma endise mentoriga peab ta valmis olema taiemahuliseks gangidevaheliseks sõjaks. Ciro on aga nainud elu kõige karmimaid palgeid, nii et tal ei ole midagi karta ega kaotada.

programme.title: 15 kusimust
programme.desc: 15 kusimust meeleolukas aastat kokku võttev erisaade on stuudiosse kutsunud saate kaks kõige suuremat fanni ja igaõhtust kaasamangijat. Omavahel võtavad mõõtu rahva oma kaitsjad Mart Juur ja Andrus Kivirahk, kel tuleb oma teadmisi naidata lõppevat aastat puudutavates kusimustes. Saadet juhib ikka Juri Butšakov.

programme.desc: Uudistemagasinide lipulaev, mis toob olulisemad ja põnevamad uudised kodumaalt ja mujalt maailmast vaatajateni Reporterile omasel mahlakal moel. Saatejuhid on alati soliidsed Jaanus Koort, Simon Suviste ja Tõnis Sarap.

programme.title: Telehommik
programme.desc: "Tere hommikust, Telehommik alustab," utlevad saatejuhid Kristjan Gold ja Romi Hasa teile Kanal 2 otsestuudiost. Kaasahaarav hommikuprogramm annab hommikule ja kogu paevale asjaliku ja praktilise ning huvitava ja positiivse stardi. Telehommik toob juba varahommikul vaatajani uudised ule Eesti!

programme.title: Eesti muusika saravaimad tipud!
programme.desc: Eesti Muusikaauhindade erisaates kuulutatakse valja EMA 2025 nominendid 16 kategoorias. Saravaid muusikalisi talente tutvustavad Kanal 2 vaatajatele Liis Lemsalu ja Kristjan Gold. Saatesse on kulla oodata ka mitmeid Eesti muusikamaailmas palavalt armastatud artiste.

programme.title: Kodus ja võõrsil
programme.desc: Mali avastab tõe Iluka kohta. Kirby kuum kohting muutub kulmaks. Bronte lisab manipulatsioonile hoogu juurde.

programme.title: Monk
programme.desc: Adrian Monk on geniaalne San Francisco politseiuurija, kes tegutseb nuud politsei erakonsultandina. Olles oma toos vaga hea, on ta samas ka veidrik, kes kannatab obsessiiv-kompulsiivse haire all. Ta on ettearvamatu ja impulsiivne inimene, kuidi samas ei jaa tal ukski asi kahe silma vahele, mis teebki temast politsei raudvara.

programme.title: Magipaastjad
programme.desc: Emili õde Jessika tuleb parast isa surma Salzburgist Ellmausse. Õdede lapsepõlv polnud roosiline, kuid nad otsustavad raakida asjad selgeks ning jatta mineviku varjud seljataha. Magipaastjad leiavad õnnetusse sattunud mehi otsides jarvepõhjast lõhkeainelaadungi ning olukord ahvardab kontrolli alt valjuda.

programme.title: Saatuslik kiri
programme.desc: Aslil ja Seheril on kaunist pulmakleidist erinev arusaam. Keegi ei oska kahtlustada, miks Seher Asli nii kiiresti omaks võttis. Ent Seheril on kõik sammud hasti labi mõeldud. Seher kasutab Aslit Alanurist vabanemiseks ara. Hatice paneb Mehmeti ja Asli laulatuse ara hoidmiseks kaiku oma viimase trumbi.

programme.title: Lena Lorenz
programme.desc: Floral on kaval mõte, kuidas oma pettusest puhtalt valja tulla, ta raagib sellest Lenale ja palub abi. Lena soovitab Markole kõik ules tunnistada. Eval on Vinzi bussifirma suhtes oma salaplaan. Julia poeg Tim ja ta pruut Celine jõuavad kohale, Julia ullatuseks on Celine rase. Julia ja Celine vahel ei teki kohe sooje tundeid.

programme.title: Naabriplika
programme.desc: Vallavanema naine tahab iseseisvuda. Selleks on loomulikult kõige lihtsam viis minna valda toole. Ka kirikõpetaja otsib tood, sest laps on ju loodud selleks, et raha kulutada. Nõnda satub vallavanem toootsijate laine alla. Aga Paavel poleks Paavel, kui ta seda probleemi vasaku varbaga ei lahendaks. Kahjuks selgub, et vallalt oodatakse hoopis uute tookohtade loomise asemel koondamisi. Esna vallas võtab maad huvide konflikt. Maakler on hadas Aliinaga, kes tema puudlustele kallistamist õppida viltu vaatab. Nõnda otsustab Maakler kaia lauda viimase trumbi - loomulikult ostab ta Aliinale mulje avaldamiseks auto. Kuid Aliinale pole sugugi kerge muljet avaldada. Isegi autoga mitte. Bussijaama lendsalk on aga kimpus selgeltnagemise ja horoskooplusega.

programme.title: Reporter
programme.desc: Uudistemagasinide lipulaev, mis toob olulisemad ja põnevamad uudised kodumaalt ja mujalt maailmast vaatajateni Reporterile omasel mahlakal moel. Saatejuhid on alati soliidsed Jaanus Koort, Simon Suviste ja Tõnis Sarap.

programme.title: 15 kusimust
programme.desc: Kodumaine strateegiline malumang, mille muudab kaasahaaravaks põnev vihjete susteem ja strateegia element. Saates on vastamisi kaks mangijat, kel on võimalus hakata panustama enda tugevustele ning samal ajal vastase nõrkusele. Mõnikord võib selline tegutsemine edu tuua, aga teinekord hoopis katte maksta ning vajalikest punktidest ilma jatta. Saadet juhib Juri Butšakov.

programme.title: Öokulaline
programme.desc: Eesti uks rikkamaid inimesi, Hansapanga ja LHV panga asutaja Rain Lõhmus elab juba enam kui 10 aastat Šveitsis, maalilise Lugano jarve kaldal. Saatejuht Mart Normet uurib, kas raha teeb õnnelikuks ja miks ikkagi Eestis hinnad nii kallid on? Lisaks LHV panga nõukogu juhtimisele panustab Rain Lõhmus suure osa oma energiast poja kasvatamisele ja tema tennisetreeningutesse. Miks on neil aga kodus robotkoer ja millist imelikku hommikusooki Lõhmuste juures pakutakse, seda ja palju muud saate kuulda ja naha tanases seikluslikus saates. Režissoor Andreas Lenk, operaator Madis Reimund, helioperaator Tanel Paats, toimetajad Sigrid Salutee ja Kairit Tsaro.

programme.title: Apteeker Melchior. Viirastus
programme.desc: Keskaegse krimipõneviku teises filmis ehmatab oovahti kohutav viirastus - rikka kaupmehe traagiliselt uppunud tutar. Hommikuks on vahimees kõrgest tornist surnuks kukkunud ja kahtlastes õnnetustes kaotavad elu veel mitu inimest. Neid sundmusi uuriva Melchiori teed ristuvad nii lõbutudruku kui preestriga, nii võõramaa kunstniku kui hullunud ketseriga. Vihjed viivad ta Pirita kloostrisse, mille sunged võlvid varjavad unustusse maetud ohtlikku saladust. Samal ajal vaevab Melchiorit mõistatus, miks ta armastatu Keterlyn uhtakki nende kihluse katkestab…

programme.title: Tipptund 2
programme.desc: Mollukomoodia teises filmis peavad Hongkongi politseinik Lee ja tema jankist kolleeg Carter kinni nabima uliohtliku kurjategija. Mehed loodavad Hongkongis korralikult valja puhata, aga paraku langeb juba esimesel õhtul nende õlule ulesanne, mis viib nad Los Angelese agulitesse ja Las Vegase tuledesarasse. Kõik selleks, et tabada kurikuulus maffiaboss ja tema surmavalt kaunis kaaslanna.

programme.title: Valelikud võrgutajad
programme.desc: Hirmus, et uber A Alit piinab, poorduvad valelikud võrgutajad abi saamiseks potentsiaalse vaenlase poole.

programme.title: Apteeker Melchior
programme.desc: Tallinnas tapetakse kuulus orduruutel Clingenstein - kangelane, kes vabastas Laanemere piraatidest. Nuud on ta pea maha raiutud ja suu munte tais topitud. Kadunud on kuldkett, mille ta alles samal paeval ostis. Kohtuharra Wenzel Dorn võtab mõrvapaigale kaasa noore apteekri Melchior Wakenstede. Noormees on nagu verekoer, kes oskavat ka surnutega raakida. Melchiori nutikus ja Dorni oskamatus viivad aga selleni, et kogu mõrvaloo lahendamine jaab apteekri õlule. Peagi selgub, et tapetud ruutel tuli Tallinnasse eriulesandega. Kõik jaljed viivad dominiiklaste kloostrisse. Sealt algab mõrvade rida, kus ohvriks kõik, kes puutunud kokku salaparase "Tallinna vangiga". Apteeker Melchiori triloogia põhineb raamatumuugi edetabelite tipust tuntud romaanisarjal. Stsenaristid Indrek Hargla, Elmo Nuganen ja Olle Mirme põimisid esimeses filmis raamatust "Apteeker Melchior ja Oleviste mõistatus" tuntud tegelased ja sundmused taiesti uute, filmi jaoks loodud keerdkaikudega.

programme.desc: Kui naine sõidab teelt valja ja sureb, leitakse tema keha salaparaselt kolm hommikut hiljem selgeltnagija poolt, kes on tuntud tõe vaanamise poolest. Monk peab avastama, kas ta raagib seekord tõtt või vastasel juhu laskma mõrvaril vabadusse jaada.

programme.title: Magipaastjad
programme.desc: Emili kavatseb oma surnud mehe leinamisega rahu teha ja laheb koos Tobiasega magimatkale. Juhtub õnnetus. Andreas leiab markmed, millest selgub matkajate asukoht. Magipaastjad asuvad paasteoperatsioonile, mis kujuneb katastoofiliseks. Algab võitlus elu ja surma peale.

programme.title: Saatuslik kiri
programme.desc: Vaid mõned minutid enne laulatust tekitab Hatice kaik Asli ja Mehmeti vahel konflikti. Hatice on pettunud, et Alanur end laulatusel ei ilmuta ega skandaali tekita. Mehmet pole arvestanud, et tal tuleb aega veeta ka Asli sõpradega. Alanur joob end tais ja rikub Asli ja Mehmeti pulmaoo.
